Package org.netbeans.swing.tabcontrol.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComplexListDataListener
    An extension to javax.swing.ListDataListener to allow handling of events on non-contiguous elements
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayDiff
    Class representing a diff of two arrays.
    ComplexListDataEvent
    An extension to ListDataEvent which can report data about non-contiguous changes to data.
    TabActionEvent
    An action event which may be consumed by a listener.
    VeryComplexListDataEvent
    Event which provides granular data on setTabs() events which may contain arbitrary differences, moves, additions and removals of array contents (or no changes at all).
